38:16.186 --> 38:19.537
Bering.

38:19.631 --> 38:21.614
Bering!

38:21.708 --> 38:25.360
♪

38:25.378 --> 38:29.380
♪

38:29.474 --> 38:33.034
I hope she's worth it.

38:33.127 --> 38:35.870
Let's go.

38:35.889 --> 38:37.939
Arias!
Back to your cell.

38:43.880 --> 38:45.322
<i> [donavan]</i>
<i> protective custody.</i>

38:45.473 --> 38:47.324
<i> "the hole".</i>

38:47.551 --> 38:53.979
♪

38:53.999 --> 38:58.501
♪

38:58.653 --> 39:01.320
<i> No communication</i>
<i> with humans,</i>

39:01.340 --> 39:04.824
