39:11.257 --> 39:16.335
♪

39:16.355 --> 39:22.692
♪

39:22.844 --> 39:24.752
[door buzzer]

39:24.771 --> 39:31.034
♪

39:31.261 --> 39:34.371
♪

39:34.598 --> 39:37.189
<i> Just one second of every</i>
