40:25.573 --> 40:26.589
[humming]

40:26.741 --> 40:28.499
"somewhere in time
I must have done

40:28.652 --> 40:30.593
An enormous amount
of good deeds

40:30.820 --> 40:33.004
To have been rewarded
with such wonderful and

40:33.156 --> 40:35.823
Selfless friends
