40:40.830 --> 40:47.444
♪

40:47.671 --> 40:52.932
♪

40:52.951 --> 40:56.786
♪

40:56.938 --> 41:00.531
"hello, my lovely friend."

41:00.625 --> 41:02.775
"I'm so grateful that you've
offered to help me

41:02.869 --> 41:03.960
When you get out."

41:04.111 --> 41:06.296
[laughing]

41:06.447 --> 41:09.782
[indistinct chatter]

41:09.876 --> 41:11.784
"I'm more determined than
