41:11.803 --> 41:13.970
Gain my freedom.

41:14.197 --> 41:16.531
You can help me
make that happen."

41:16.549 --> 41:21.202
♪

41:21.221 --> 41:23.554
"I'd like to know what is
being posted online on

41:23.648 --> 41:26.632
Some specific personal
social media pages.

41:26.726 --> 41:28.300
I will send you
a list of names,

41:28.320 --> 41:30.712
Including travis'
