41:50.491 --> 41:52.083
But don't you dare give up.

41:52.177 --> 41:54.010
Love you and miss you.

41:54.161 --> 41:56.921
Your songbird."

41:57.015 --> 42:00.424
"thinking of what good
friends you are makes me cry,

42:00.519 --> 42:03.077
And crying is something
I don't do often anymore

42:03.096 --> 42:04.837
As I've gone numb
since being hit with

42:04.856 --> 42:07.098
One traumatic event
after another."

42:07.250 --> 42:11.027
[grunting & coughing]

42:11.254 --> 42:14.030
[indistinct chatter]
yeah, get her!

42:14.257 --> 42:16.348
[indistinct chatter
& grunting]

42:16.368 --> 42:18.201
Yeah, get her!

42:18.428 --> 42:19.852
Rosie!

42:19.946 --> 42:22.872
[echoing footsteps]

42:23.099 --> 42:26.434
One word...

42:26.452 --> 42:30.362
One word...

42:30.456 --> 42:32.197
You're both dead.

42:32.217 --> 42:36.110
♪

42:36.129 --> 42:41.465
♪

42:41.618 --> 42:44.619
[crying]

42:44.637 --> 42:47.789
[sobbing]

42:47.807 --> 42:53.736
[humming]

42:53.888 --> 42:55.905
[indistinct chatter
in distance]

42:56.132 --> 43:00.301
[singing quietly]
amazing grace...

43:00.320 --> 43:06.583
♪

43:06.810 --> 43:09.644
[guard] brown, roll up,
you're moving out.

43:09.737 --> 43:11.312
<i> After tracy's sentencing,</i>

43:11.331 --> 43:13.481
<i> She was transferred</i>
<i> to perryville prison</i>

43:13.499 --> 43:15.817
<i> To serve out the</i>
<i> remainder of her ten years.</i>

43:15.910 --> 43:19.095
Let me say goodbye
to donavan.

43:19.246 --> 43:23.007
[guard] let's go.

43:23.101 --> 43:25.101
<i> I knew there was a</i>
<i> good chance I wasn't</i>

43:25.328 --> 43:29.013
<i> Going to be able to</i>
<i> see her for years.</i>

43:29.165 --> 43:31.015
I love you,
donavan bering!

43:31.109 --> 43:33.592
I love you too!

43:33.612 --> 43:38.281
♪

43:38.508 --> 43:41.767
♪

43:41.786 --> 43:47.790
[crying]

43:48.017 --> 43:52.111
♪

43:52.130 --> 43:55.356
♪

43:55.375 --> 43:57.634
<i> Not long after,</i>
<i> they released me.</i>

43:57.861 --> 44:00.878
<i> But I would never</i>
<i> be the same.</i>

44:00.972 --> 44:03.047
<i> Jail changed me.</i>

44:03.141 --> 44:04.456
<i> It didn't make me feel</i>
<i> remorse for failing to</i>

44:04.476 --> 44:06.384
<i> Report a crime</i>
<i> when I should've.</i>

44:06.478 --> 44:08.552
<i> I carried plenty of</i>
<i> remorse long before</i>

44:08.705 --> 44:09.812
<i> I was put behind bars.</i>

44:09.964 --> 44:11.389
[door buzzer]

44:11.541 --> 44:15.059
[mechanical whirring]

44:15.211 --> 44:17.395
<i> Jail made me mistrust</i>
<i> a system that</i>

44:17.489 --> 44:20.156
<i> Treats people like us way</i>
<i> differently than the</i>

44:20.307 --> 44:22.900
<i> Sheriff's rich</i>
<i> hunting buddies.</i>

44:23.052 --> 44:24.902
<i> More than anything,</i>

44:24.996 --> 44:28.665
<i> Jail made me want to hold</i>
<i> those I loved close and</i>

44:28.892 --> 44:30.983
<i> Fight for them</i>
<i> with everything in me.</i>

44:31.002 --> 44:36.172
♪

44:36.399 --> 44:42.327
♪

44:42.347 --> 44:47.758
♪

44:47.852 --> 44:50.335
It's lies, all of it.

44:50.355 --> 44:52.355
I know her,
jodi's a good person.

44:52.582 --> 44:54.582
She would never-
you don't know her!

44:54.600 --> 45:01.013
♪

45:01.032 --> 45:04.425
♪

45:04.444 --> 45:06.035
[sighing]

45:10.041 --> 45:13.951
[phone ringing]

45:14.045 --> 45:18.197
[phone ringing]

45:18.216 --> 45:19.607
Hello?

45:19.625 --> 45:20.791
[phone] you have a
call from the arizona

45:20.944 --> 45:23.627
Department of corrections,
estrella jail.

45:23.780 --> 45:25.370
To accept the
call from inmate-

45:25.465 --> 45:26.872
[jodi] jodi arias-

45:26.891 --> 45:27.873
[automated message]
press 2.

45:27.892 --> 45:29.450
[phone beeping]

45:29.469 --> 45:31.302
[automated message]
this call is being recorded.

45:31.396 --> 45:32.711
Songbird!

45:32.731 --> 45:35.957
[jodi] oh, I really wish I
could hug you right now!

45:36.050 --> 45:37.975
It's unbearable without you!

45:38.127 --> 45:40.552
[indistinct chatter]

45:40.646 --> 45:42.572
I sent some letters to your
house, did you get them?

45:45.059 --> 45:47.059
Probably.

45:47.078 --> 45:48.745
I saw you on magazines,
on tabloids,

45:48.972 --> 45:50.729
There are so many of them.
You're everywhere.

45:50.749 --> 45:52.582
How did I look?

45:52.809 --> 45:55.326
The things they're
saying are awful.

45:55.420 --> 45:58.829
Are there any pictures
of me when I was blond?

45:58.982 --> 46:01.999
Travis loved my
hair that way.

46:02.093 --> 46:03.593
[jodi] when I found out I
was gonna be arrested,

46:03.820 --> 46:05.762
I had to dye it
back to my natural.

46:05.913 --> 46:07.764
No way I was just gonna let
it grow out and end up with

46:07.915 --> 46:09.599
A two-tone mess.

46:09.826 --> 46:13.269
Can you imagine me doing
interviews like that?

46:13.496 --> 46:15.104
I guess not.

46:15.331 --> 46:16.922
Look for the first
letter I sent.

46:17.016 --> 46:19.192
[jodi] I drew a
songbird on it.

46:24.765 --> 46:26.674
Oh, I got it.

46:26.692 --> 46:28.785
I need you to get in touch
with some people for me.

46:34.700 --> 46:36.867
-Who are they?
-Friends!

46:37.020 --> 46:38.544
People who can help.

46:43.134 --> 46:45.284
[sighing]

46:45.303 --> 46:48.045
♪

46:48.197 --> 46:50.381
<i> Jodi never told me</i>
<i> how she knew them.</i>

46:50.475 --> 46:52.533
<i> I thought they were</i>
<i> old friends of hers.</i>

46:52.552 --> 46:57.963
♪

46:57.982 --> 47:01.317
<i> They weren't.</i>

47:01.468 --> 47:03.802
<i> They were new friends,</i>
<i> like me,</i>

47:03.822 --> 47:05.137
<i> Who believed in her</i>
<i> innocence and</i>

47:05.156 --> 47:07.064
<i> Were willing to help</i>
<i> her prove it.</i>

47:07.158 --> 47:09.066
Hello, is this lukas?

47:09.218 --> 47:11.994
<i> Lukas was a computer</i>
<i> genius in germany.</i>

47:12.146 --> 47:13.830
<i> He'd written a program that</i>
<i> had made him enough money</i>

47:14.057 --> 47:15.739
<i> To spend his time</i>
<i> on his hobbies,</i>

47:15.834 --> 47:17.741
<i> Like helping an accused</i>
<i> american murderer</i>

47:17.894 --> 47:19.985
<i> Prove her innocence.</i>

47:20.079 --> 47:23.064
<i> Whatever jodi needed</i>
<i> researched, he was her guy.</i>

47:23.157 --> 47:25.232
<i> There was a lawyer</i>
<i> from miami</i>

47:25.251 --> 47:27.677
<i> Who I only knew by his</i>
<i> last name, olek.</i>

47:27.828 --> 47:29.753
<i> Whenever jodi wasn't sure</i>
<i> her own lawyers were</i>

47:29.906 --> 47:31.496
<i> Making the best decisions,</i>

47:31.516 --> 47:34.499
<i> Olek came to the rescue</i>
<i> with his legal expertise.</i>

47:34.519 --> 47:36.519
<i> There were the</i>
<i> becks in new york.</i>

47:36.670 --> 47:39.413
<i> They were great at drumming</i>
<i> up even more supporters.</i>

47:39.506 --> 47:41.023
<i> Whenever jodi</i>
<i> needed anything,</i>

47:41.175 --> 47:43.601
<i> All it took was one call</i>
<i> and they'd be there.</i>

47:43.695 --> 47:47.346
<i> That was just the</i>
<i> beginning of team arias.</i>

47:47.365 --> 47:51.516
<i> All of us dedicated</i>
<i> to saving jodi.</i>

47:51.536 --> 47:53.094
When you were released
from prison and

47:53.187 --> 47:55.446
You began working
for jodi arias,

47:55.598 --> 47:56.931
Did you believe she
was innocent of the

47:57.024 --> 47:58.875
Murder of travis alexander?

47:59.102 --> 48:03.045
Yes.

48:03.197 --> 48:05.214
Was she innocent?

48:05.441 --> 48:07.383
Hell no.

48:07.610 --> 48:13.538
♪

48:13.558 --> 48:18.561
♪

48:18.712 --> 48:20.879
[clanging]

48:20.899 --> 48:23.791
<i> While I was trying</i>
<i> to restart my life,</i>

48:23.809 --> 48:29.130
<i> Tracy was facing a new,</i>
<i> much tougher prison.</i>

48:29.223 --> 48:31.390
<i> And she was doing it alone.</i>

48:31.409 --> 48:35.894
♪

48:35.914 --> 48:41.083
♪

48:41.310 --> 48:42.810
<i> For me, helping jodi</i>
<i> was becoming</i>

48:42.828 --> 48:45.237
<i> My whole world.</i>

48:45.256 --> 48:47.089
♪

48:47.316 --> 48:49.166
<i> My new job was finding a</i>
<i> publisher for the book</i>

48:49.260 --> 48:51.076
<i> Jodi had been writing</i>
<i> about herself and</i>

48:51.095 --> 48:54.597
<i> Getting her own words out</i>
<i> there on social media.</i>

48:54.748 --> 48:57.491
[phone: Jodi] I am so
grateful for every letter,

48:57.584 --> 49:00.436
Comma,
postcard, comma...

49:00.587 --> 49:02.663
Are you getting this?

49:02.756 --> 49:07.017
"every letter,
comma, postcard-"

49:07.170 --> 49:09.186
It's my name, donavan.

49:09.280 --> 49:12.339
No spelling errors,
no missing punctuation.

49:12.433 --> 49:13.783
If you make any mistakes,

49:14.010 --> 49:15.859
I'm the one that
looks like an idiot.

49:16.012 --> 49:18.362
I cannot look stupid.

49:18.456 --> 49:20.605
Ever. Understand?

49:20.700 --> 49:22.941
I'm being careful,
I promise.

49:22.961 --> 49:25.186
<i> At first, the posts</i>
<i> were harmless,</i>

49:25.204 --> 49:27.021
<i> And I was happy to</i>
<i> help my friend.</i>

49:27.114 --> 49:28.022
<i> Pretty soon</i>
<i> she was calling me</i>

49:28.115 --> 49:30.615
<i> With instructions every day.</i>

49:30.635 --> 49:32.951
<i> Then twice a day,</i>
<i> sometimes more.</i>

49:32.971 --> 49:36.714
[phone ringing]

49:36.866 --> 49:40.384
Hello?
This is donavan.

49:40.478 --> 49:42.794
Yes, I know jodi arias.

49:42.814 --> 49:45.314
Yep, 4pm, I can.

49:52.306 --> 49:54.490
They want to interview me.

49:54.717 --> 49:56.050
Who?

49:56.068 --> 49:58.385
One of the news stations.
I don't want to be on tv.

49:58.404 --> 50:00.145
Think about how much
it'll help my case

50:00.164 --> 50:01.905
For people to
hear the truth.

50:02.058 --> 50:03.741
[sighing] I don't know,
I'm not like you.

50:03.835 --> 50:05.392
I'm not comfortable
in front of a camera.

50:05.486 --> 50:06.836
[jodi] oh, you'll be great.

50:06.987 --> 50:09.913
I thank god for you
every day,

50:10.008 --> 50:12.733
You know that, right?

50:12.752 --> 50:15.586
[sighing]

50:15.738 --> 50:19.331
Jodi is smart,
she's generous.

50:19.350 --> 50:22.184
She wouldn't hurt a fly,
let alone someone she loved.

50:22.411 --> 50:24.595
She told me that intruders
in black masks

50:24.689 --> 50:27.672
Broke into his house,
a male and a female.

50:27.692 --> 50:29.433
I'm not sure if
they were there

50:29.585 --> 50:32.177
As a robbery gone wrong,

50:32.196 --> 50:34.938
Or if they intended to hurt
him for whatever reason.

50:35.033 --> 50:40.185
Luckily, jodi escaped without
them killing her, too.

50:40.279 --> 50:44.098
People see the front page of
the tabloids and they assume

50:44.116 --> 50:47.043
They know what happened,
but they don't.

50:47.194 --> 50:48.693
I know jodi.

50:48.713 --> 50:52.548
Everything about her
is love and not hate.

50:52.699 --> 50:56.719
Fired for what?

50:56.946 --> 50:59.204
Going on tv, supporting
someone who's innocent

50:59.298 --> 51:02.950
Until proven guilty?

51:02.968 --> 51:05.377
You know I work hard here.

51:05.396 --> 51:07.879
This isn't fair.

51:07.899 --> 51:12.551
♪

51:12.570 --> 51:15.312
[phone ringing]

51:15.464 --> 51:16.480
Hey.

51:16.632 --> 51:18.056
What are you doing, dov?

51:18.076 --> 51:19.891
You're defending
murderers now?

51:19.911 --> 51:22.319
-No, I...
-We saw you on tv!

51:22.471 --> 51:25.155
-Mom did too.
-Jodi's my friend.

51:25.308 --> 51:26.398
I know that she
didn't do any-

51:26.417 --> 51:28.084
[brother] how can you still
be so gullible?

51:28.235 --> 51:30.920
You've already been to jail
for trusting the wrong person.

51:31.071 --> 51:33.238
-Didn't you learn a thing?
-This is different.

51:33.332 --> 51:34.665
[brother] damn right it is!

51:34.759 --> 51:36.667
Do I need to call your
probation officer to

51:36.819 --> 51:38.335
Save you from yourself?

51:38.487 --> 51:40.504
[donavan] but I haven't
done anything wrong.

51:40.656 --> 51:42.005
Jodi's not a
convicted felon,

51:42.100 --> 51:43.415
I'm allowed to talk to
her without violating

51:43.434 --> 51:45.008
My probation.

51:45.161 --> 51:49.588
Do you have any idea
how much she's hated?

51:49.682 --> 51:53.834
You seriously want to be on
the receiving end of that?

51:53.853 --> 51:56.428
I've been on the receiving
end of hate my whole life!

51:56.447 --> 51:58.447
"freak! Dyke!"

51:58.674 --> 52:00.116
And what, when the kids
were coming after you,

52:00.343 --> 52:01.342
You didn't mind me
standing up to

52:01.435 --> 52:02.526
The bullies then,
did you?

52:02.620 --> 52:04.436
That's not the same
thing and you know it.

52:04.455 --> 52:07.939
It is to me,
jodi is a victim too.

52:07.959 --> 52:11.352
♪

52:11.445 --> 52:13.704
Look, I love you,
but you're choosing

52:13.856 --> 52:15.631
Jodi arias over your family.

52:15.858 --> 52:17.633
Oh, please.

52:17.784 --> 52:20.210
[brother] I've got to watch
out for my kids, dov.

52:20.363 --> 52:24.865
Don't call me,
don't call mom.

52:24.958 --> 52:27.792
We didn't want this,
but we're done.

52:27.812 --> 52:30.462
We're just done.

52:30.481 --> 52:36.043
♪

52:36.061 --> 52:39.638
[sighing]

52:39.657 --> 52:44.976
♪

52:44.996 --> 52:47.404
♪

52:47.498 --> 52:50.224
<i> [donavan] life was about to</i>
<i> get harder for tracy, too.</i>

52:50.242 --> 52:54.503
♪

52:54.730 --> 52:58.823
♪

52:58.843 --> 53:01.177
Does that say,
"jodi arias"?

53:01.404 --> 53:03.679
♪

53:10.170 --> 53:11.578
[guard] open 7-1-3.

53:11.672 --> 53:13.580
[buzzer &
door opening]

53:13.599 --> 53:15.691
♪

53:15.918 --> 53:17.193
What's going on?
What are you doing?

53:17.420 --> 53:18.694
Turn around!
Hands behind your back!

53:18.845 --> 53:22.756
[panicked breathing]

53:22.775 --> 53:24.349
Tell me, just tell me
what's happening!

53:24.368 --> 53:26.702
I didn't do anything! Please,
I didn't do anything!

53:26.853 --> 53:28.871
Where are you taking me?

53:29.022 --> 53:31.523
♪ [suspenseful] ♪

53:31.542 --> 53:37.213
♪

53:42.887 --> 53:44.795
Why am I here?

53:44.947 --> 53:46.371
When was the last
time you communicated

53:46.465 --> 53:48.298
With donavan bering?

53:48.451 --> 53:50.226
What is this about?

53:50.453 --> 53:51.301
Are you gonna answer
the question or

53:51.454 --> 53:53.620
Am I gonna write you up?

53:53.639 --> 53:55.046
When was the last time
you communicated

53:55.140 --> 53:58.216
With donavan bering?

53:58.236 --> 54:01.979
She was on the
approved visitors list.

54:02.131 --> 54:04.240
Then she got removed.

54:04.467 --> 54:06.149
I guess you'll have to see
her like the rest of us,

54:06.244 --> 54:10.228
On tv.

54:10.248 --> 54:12.897
Let's talk about
your tattoos.

54:12.917 --> 54:15.084
I had them all
when I got here.

54:15.311 --> 54:17.419
What about the one with
the murderer's name on it?

54:29.767 --> 54:33.251
This facility operates
under my rules.

54:33.345 --> 54:36.921
And only my rules.

54:37.016 --> 54:38.832
Whatever plans you're putting
in place for jodi arias,

54:38.925 --> 54:41.259
Abandon them now
and save yourself.

54:41.353 --> 54:43.595
I'm not planning anything.

54:43.614 --> 54:46.282
When was the last time
arias contacted you?

54:46.509 --> 54:48.767
-She sends me letters.
-About what?

54:48.861 --> 54:50.786
I don't know.
Pep talks,

54:51.013 --> 54:52.846
"hang in there,"
that kind of stuff.

54:52.865 --> 54:53.864
What does she ask
you to do for her?

54:53.958 --> 54:55.124
Nothing!

54:55.275 --> 54:57.126
You call her songbird?

54:57.277 --> 55:00.037
She sings a lot.

55:00.189 --> 55:01.780
Who else does
she know here?

55:01.799 --> 55:03.465
I don't know!

55:03.692 --> 55:05.634
We know what she's
up to at estrella.

55:05.861 --> 55:08.211
And she's not gonna
get away with it here.

55:08.306 --> 55:13.200
[laughing]

55:13.218 --> 55:15.960
Oh my god,

55:15.980 --> 55:18.889
You're actually afraid
of jodi arias.

55:18.983 --> 55:24.153
[laughing]

55:24.304 --> 55:27.806
You best think about how many
years you got left in here.

55:27.825 --> 55:30.642
How hard do you
want them to be?

55:30.661 --> 55:32.052
If she's sending
you instructions,

55:32.071 --> 55:33.236
If she's laying the
groundwork for an

55:33.389 --> 55:36.314
Escape attempt, we will
find out about it.

55:36.408 --> 55:38.575
And as god as my
witness, brown,

55:38.669 --> 55:40.169
You'll regret the day you
ever heard the name

55:40.396 --> 55:42.245
Jodi arias.

55:42.398 --> 55:44.823
Or had it permanently
etched in your skin.

55:44.842 --> 55:51.013
♪

55:51.240 --> 55:54.758
The jodi I know would
never have harmed travis.

55:54.852 --> 55:56.668
While jodi sits in jail,

55:56.687 --> 55:59.188
The intruders are free
to murder again.

55:59.415 --> 56:01.431
Why are you not
talking about them?

56:01.584 --> 56:04.601
<i> I'd spent months</i>
<i> doing jodi's bidding.</i>

56:04.753 --> 56:06.770
<i> Posting whatever she wanted.</i>

56:06.922 --> 56:09.423
<i> Getting messages</i>
<i> to team arias.</i>

56:09.441 --> 56:12.183
<i> And coordinating</i>
<i> with jodi's mom.</i>

56:12.203 --> 56:14.370
<i> By the time I finally met</i>
<i> her parents in person,</i>

56:14.597 --> 56:16.038
<i> I'd spent so much time</i>
<i> talking to them</i>

56:16.189 --> 56:17.948
<i> On the phone, they already</i>
<i> felt like family.</i>

56:18.100 --> 56:21.118
At last!

56:21.212 --> 56:23.361
Oh...

56:23.381 --> 56:26.715
♪

56:26.867 --> 56:30.611
Come on in, hun.

56:30.629 --> 56:32.796
Donavan...

56:32.948 --> 56:35.039
Oh, no, no, no,
it's okay.

56:35.059 --> 56:38.802
♪

56:38.954 --> 56:42.956
Thank you for everything
you're doing for us.

56:43.049 --> 56:45.567
They haven't
found us here yet.

56:45.794 --> 56:46.885
Who?

56:46.904 --> 56:50.981
Oh, you know,
all of them.

56:51.133 --> 56:54.392
We had to shut down our
restaurant for good.

56:54.486 --> 56:56.561
Every week, more...

56:56.580 --> 56:59.230
Broken windows,
more threats.

56:59.250 --> 57:00.916
They found my
mother's house.

57:01.067 --> 57:02.251
Told her they were
going do to her

57:02.402 --> 57:04.645
What was done to travis.

57:04.738 --> 57:06.922
She's in her 80s,
it's just not right.

57:07.149 --> 57:10.259
It doesn't matter if we
change our phone number.

57:10.410 --> 57:14.746
They find us.
I don't know how.

57:14.765 --> 57:16.823
We live in fear.

57:16.917 --> 57:19.676
Fear that their
threats are real.

57:19.770 --> 57:21.828
Fear that they're gonna
find our daughter guilty and

57:21.922 --> 57:26.925
Sentence her to...
[crying]

57:27.019 --> 57:31.354
Jodi's difficult, we know.

57:31.507 --> 57:32.948
We're not blind
to who she is.

57:33.175 --> 57:36.026
Bill...

57:36.120 --> 57:39.955
She's no angel.

57:40.106 --> 57:42.106
But she's still our child.

57:42.126 --> 57:46.703
♪

57:46.855 --> 57:49.465
You know I'm here to
help any way I can.

57:49.616 --> 57:53.026
I'm not going anywhere.

57:53.045 --> 57:55.286
<i> After my own family</i>
<i> had disowned me,</i>

57:55.380 --> 57:57.956
<i> I needed jodi's parents</i>
<i> as much as they needed me.</i>

57:57.975 --> 58:01.977
♪

58:02.204 --> 58:04.980
<i> They were afraid</i>
<i> of jodi arias.</i>

58:05.131 --> 58:06.540
What are you looking for?

58:06.558 --> 58:08.484
<i> Tracy paid the price.</i>

58:08.635 --> 58:11.820
♪ [suspenseful] ♪

58:12.047 --> 58:16.399
♪

58:16.552 --> 58:18.494
Oh, hey, that's my wife!

58:18.721 --> 58:20.403
Please don't, please,
please don't, please,

58:20.498 --> 58:22.313
It's all I have.

58:22.333 --> 58:27.503
♪

58:27.730 --> 58:32.657
♪

58:32.676 --> 58:34.084
[phone ringing]

58:34.178 --> 58:35.493
Hello?

58:35.587 --> 58:38.071
Tracy needs to talk to you,
I'll put her through.

58:38.090 --> 58:40.924
[tracy] donavan, you need
to stop helping jodi.

58:41.076 --> 58:42.576
What's going on,
are you okay?

58:42.594 --> 58:44.261
[tracy] they keep
searching my cell.

58:44.355 --> 58:46.596
They won't stop.

58:46.749 --> 58:48.431
They're looking for
anything from jodi.

58:48.584 --> 58:50.508
Tell her to stop
writing to me.

58:50.602 --> 58:53.695
You should stop
helping her too.

58:53.922 --> 58:56.848
Trust me, you need to
walk away from this.

58:56.867 --> 58:59.517
♪

58:59.537 --> 59:02.287
I can't.

59:10.714 --> 59:13.048
[phone] this call
is being recorded.

59:13.199 --> 59:14.608
[donovan] songbird.

59:14.626 --> 59:16.534
I need to ask you a favor.

59:16.554 --> 59:17.886
Okay.

59:18.038 --> 59:19.963
[jodi] I know you believe in
the power of prayer.

59:20.057 --> 59:22.783
And I'm sure you pray for me
each and every day and

59:22.876 --> 59:25.802
I'm endlessly
grateful for that.

59:25.954 --> 59:30.065
[indistinct chatter]

59:30.292 --> 59:33.977
As you know,
my trial is coming up.

59:34.071 --> 59:36.479
I'm asking that you set
aside a special day for

59:36.574 --> 59:41.726
The purpose of praying
and fasting for me.

59:41.820 --> 59:45.581
♪ [suspenseful] ♪

59:45.732 --> 59:48.900
Can you do that for me?

59:48.919 --> 59:50.586
Donavan?

59:50.737 --> 59:52.754
Sure, of course.

59:52.981 --> 59:57.984
♪

59:58.003 --> 1:00:03.323
♪

1:00:03.342 --> 1:00:10.254
♪

1:00:10.274 --> 1:00:12.590
♪

1:00:12.610 --> 1:00:14.776
[door opening]

1:00:16.930 --> 1:00:20.115
[indistinct shouting
continues]

1:00:26.365 --> 1:00:28.624
They're threatening us!
Do something!

1:00:32.445 --> 1:00:35.355
[indistinct chatter]

1:00:35.374 --> 1:00:40.469
♪

1:00:40.620 --> 1:00:41.953
<i> [donavan]</i>
<i> on that first day,</i>

1:00:41.972 --> 1:00:45.198
<i> I didn't care about anything</i>
<i> the prosecution said.</i>

1:00:45.217 --> 1:00:48.551
<i> It was their job to</i>
<i> prove jodi's guilt...</i>

1:00:48.646 --> 1:00:50.962
<i> We knew that.</i>

1:00:51.056 --> 1:00:53.464
[indistinct chatter]

1:00:53.484 --> 1:00:57.653
♪

1:01:01.383 --> 1:01:04.159
<i> But when jodi's own lawyer</i>
<i> gave her opening statement,</i>

1:01:04.310 --> 1:01:07.387
<i> It took everything in me</i>
<i> not to stand up and scream.</i>

1:01:07.406 --> 1:01:10.832
Jodi arias killed
travis alexander.

1:01:10.984 --> 1:01:13.743
[indistinct chatter]

1:01:13.896 --> 1:01:16.171
There is no question about it.

1:01:19.159 --> 1:01:21.918
The million-dollar question...

1:01:22.070 --> 1:01:26.423
It's, what would have
forced her to do it?

1:01:26.575 --> 1:01:29.075
And throughout this trial,
you will hear

1:01:29.169 --> 1:01:32.095
That jodi was indeed forced.

1:01:32.247 --> 1:01:34.338
<i> I didn't hear anything else.</i>

1:01:34.358 --> 1:01:37.842
♪

1:01:37.861 --> 1:01:42.364
[phone ringing]

1:01:44.868 --> 1:01:46.350
[phone] you have a call from
the arizona department

1:01:46.370 --> 1:01:48.778
Of corrections,
estrella jail.

1:01:48.931 --> 1:01:50.354
To accept the
call from inmate-

1:01:50.449 --> 1:01:51.689
[jodi] jodi arias-

1:01:51.783 --> 1:01:56.360
[automated message]
press 2.

1:01:56.380 --> 1:01:57.879
[phone beeping]

1:01:58.031 --> 1:02:00.290
[automated message]
this call is being recorded.

1:02:00.384 --> 1:02:02.033
[jodi] donavan?

1:02:02.052 --> 1:02:07.371
♪

1:02:07.391 --> 1:02:09.299
I know you're probably
angry right now.

1:02:09.393 --> 1:02:12.802
And I can't blame you.

1:02:12.896 --> 1:02:15.063
I need you to know that I
didn't tell you everything

1:02:15.215 --> 1:02:18.716
Because I was ashamed.

1:02:18.736 --> 1:02:21.069
And I didn't want you,
of all people,

1:02:21.221 --> 1:02:24.072
To think less of me.

1:02:24.224 --> 1:02:26.241
I was worried that if I told
you what really happened,

1:02:26.392 --> 1:02:28.635
I'd lose you.

1:02:28.653 --> 1:02:33.156
And I can handle a lot,
but not that.

1:02:33.308 --> 1:02:36.567
All my life, whenever
I heard a story of

1:02:36.587 --> 1:02:40.330
Some woman whose
husband was abusive,

1:02:40.424 --> 1:02:44.593
I could never understand
why she wouldn't just leave.

1:02:44.744 --> 1:02:48.004
How she could suffer through
that kind of abuse and then,

1:02:48.098 --> 1:02:49.598
Get into bed with him at
the end of the day and

1:02:49.749 --> 1:02:52.842
Cry herself to sleep.

1:02:52.995 --> 1:02:56.679
I never understood it...

1:02:56.774 --> 1:03:01.276
Until the one crying
herself to sleep was me.

1:03:01.427 --> 1:03:04.854
If it was up to me, none of
this would be coming out now.

1:03:05.007 --> 1:03:08.024
I don't want people
to think less of him.

1:03:08.118 --> 1:03:10.619
And I don't want people
to see that I was weak,

1:03:10.770 --> 1:03:15.957
That I let that happen to me,
let it get that far.

1:03:16.184 --> 1:03:18.442
But...

1:03:18.537 --> 1:03:20.870
My lawyers tell me that the
only way to save my life

1:03:20.964 --> 1:03:24.524
Is to tell the truth.

1:03:24.543 --> 1:03:26.026
<i> When jodi dropped the</i>
<i> intruder theory and</i>

1:03:26.044 --> 1:03:28.637
<i> Claimed self-defense,</i>
<i> I had to accept that</i>

1:03:28.864 --> 1:03:31.548
<i> She was capable of</i>
<i> murder after all.</i>

1:03:31.700 --> 1:03:34.976
<i> I was shocked,</i>
<i> I was angry,</i>

1:03:35.128 --> 1:03:37.720
<i> But I knew one thing from</i>
<i> my own experience.</i>

1:03:37.873 --> 1:03:39.147
<i> When somebody tells you</i>
<i> they're a victim</i>

1:03:39.299 --> 1:03:41.149
<i> Of domestic abuse...</i>

1:03:41.301 --> 1:03:45.562
<i> You believe them.</i>

1:03:45.656 --> 1:03:48.806
<i> I was back on team arias,</i>
<i> believing jodi,</i>

1:03:48.900 --> 1:03:50.884
<i> Supporting her parents.</i>

1:03:50.902 --> 1:03:54.478
<i> But the details of the</i>
<i> crime would test us all.</i>

1:03:54.498 --> 1:03:56.239
<i> He was stabbed</i>
<i> so many times,</i>

1:03:56.333 --> 1:03:59.242
<i> The coroner couldn't even</i>
<i> make sure of the count.</i>

1:03:59.394 --> 1:04:03.079
<i> Then a shot to the head,</i>
<i>and a final cut to the throat.</i>

1:04:03.231 --> 1:04:05.006
<i> As one of the</i>
<i> experts described it,</i>

1:04:05.233 --> 1:04:09.177
<i> She had killed</i>
<i> travis three times.</i>

1:04:09.329 --> 1:04:11.571
<i> One minute it was</i>
<i> horrific autopsy photos,</i>

1:04:11.590 --> 1:04:13.256
<i> And the next...</i>

1:04:13.350 --> 1:04:14.999
<i> A sex tape.</i>

1:04:15.018 --> 1:04:18.169
[tape: Jodi]
oh, travis...

1:04:18.188 --> 1:04:20.856
You make me feel so dirty.
[moaning]

1:04:21.007 --> 1:04:25.176
[hushed chatter]

1:04:25.270 --> 1:04:28.088
<i> They'd spent months</i>
<i> harassing tracy about jodi,</i>

1:04:28.106 --> 1:04:32.092
<i> Writing her up for</i>
<i> no good reason.</i>

1:04:32.185 --> 1:04:33.869
<i> Locked down</i>
<i> 23 hours a day,</i>

1:04:34.020 --> 1:04:36.354
<i> No phone calls,</i>
<i> no visitors.</i>

1:04:36.373 --> 1:04:41.042
<i> All for what,</i>
<i> knowing jodi arias?</i>

1:04:41.269 --> 1:04:42.452
[jodi] I need you to tweet
that travis liked

1:04:42.546 --> 1:04:45.213
Looking at little boys in
their underwear.

1:04:45.365 --> 1:04:46.956
I don't know.

1:04:47.109 --> 1:04:48.532
It'll help my case
if people know

1:04:48.552 --> 1:04:50.293
What kind
of person he was.

1:04:50.387 --> 1:04:52.036
I can't post that.

1:04:52.130 --> 1:04:53.722
[jodi] sure you can.

1:04:56.618 --> 1:05:01.304
Fine,
say it's a rumor then.

1:05:01.398 --> 1:05:04.232
I designed a domestic
abuse survivor t-shirt.

1:05:04.384 --> 1:05:06.292
We can sell them on one of
my supporter pages and

1:05:06.311 --> 1:05:09.404
Donate the proceeds to a
women's charity.

1:05:09.631 --> 1:05:11.722
I need you to find
one we can work with.

1:05:11.816 --> 1:05:15.485
Also, talk to lukas and see
who's running this website

1:05:15.637 --> 1:05:19.080
"justice for travis."

1:05:19.232 --> 1:05:21.157
I sent you a list of some of
the people supporting that

1:05:21.251 --> 1:05:24.419
We need to make sure look
blocked on all my pages.

1:05:24.570 --> 1:05:25.828
Oh, and get that
list to the becks,

1:05:25.923 --> 1:05:27.756
They can check them out.

1:05:27.907 --> 1:05:30.926
We need to go after them.

1:05:31.077 --> 1:05:33.002
Oh, and talk to my mom,

1:05:33.155 --> 1:05:35.505
And tell her to put more
money on my phone.

1:05:35.599 --> 1:05:37.248
And commissary.

1:05:37.267 --> 1:05:39.583
I'm dying for
some chocolate.

1:05:39.603 --> 1:05:42.103
♪

1:05:42.330 --> 1:05:45.440
<i> I should've</i>
<i> listened to tracy,</i>

1:05:45.667 --> 1:05:47.758
<i> But I still believed</i>
<i> jody was a victim.</i>

1:05:47.778 --> 1:05:50.779
♪

1:05:55.268 --> 1:05:57.527
[lawyer] did you kill
travis alexander

1:05:57.621 --> 1:06:03.016
On June 4th, 2008?

1:06:03.034 --> 1:06:05.609
Yes, I did.

1:06:05.629 --> 1:06:07.963
[lawyer] why?

1:06:08.190 --> 1:06:10.707
The simple answer is
that he attacked me,

1:06:10.859 --> 1:06:12.542
And I defended myself.

1:06:12.636 --> 1:06:14.469
<i> [donavan] after sticking</i>
<i> with jodi so long,</i>

1:06:14.620 --> 1:06:16.287
<i> She must've thought there</i>
<i> was nothing she could say</i>

1:06:16.381 --> 1:06:19.048
<i> Or do that would make me</i>
<i> change my mind about her.</i>

1:06:19.142 --> 1:06:20.533
<i> She was wrong.</i>

1:06:20.626 --> 1:06:21.701
Let's back it up a little and

1:06:21.794 --> 1:06:26.206
Talk about your
immediate family.

1:06:26.224 --> 1:06:30.210
My mom began to carry a
wooden spoon in her purse.

1:06:30.228 --> 1:06:33.563
She would beat me with it.

1:06:33.657 --> 1:06:37.659
Every single day.

1:06:37.810 --> 1:06:39.736
It was a wooden kitchen
spoon that she would carry

1:06:39.888 --> 1:06:41.738
In her purse and if we
were misbehaving,

1:06:41.832 --> 1:06:43.890
She would use it on us.

1:06:43.983 --> 1:06:47.485
[lawyer]
when you say, "use it"?

1:06:47.579 --> 1:06:50.230
She would hit us with it.

1:06:50.323 --> 1:06:53.233
It felt pretty hard,
it left welts.

1:06:53.251 --> 1:06:55.176
Sometimes she would
beat me so hard,

1:06:55.328 --> 1:06:58.162
It would break in half.

1:06:58.181 --> 1:07:00.406
What happened when you
were ten years old?

1:07:00.425 --> 1:07:07.171
♪

1:07:07.190 --> 1:07:08.523
I think that's the
first year my dad

1:07:08.674 --> 1:07:10.933
Started to use a belt.

1:07:11.028 --> 1:07:15.179
I had so many bruises
and welts on my body...

1:07:15.198 --> 1:07:17.423
That I had to wear a long
-sleeved shirt and pants

1:07:17.517 --> 1:07:19.534
To school just to hide 'em.

1:07:19.685 --> 1:07:22.520
Did he leave welts?

1:07:22.539 --> 1:07:26.783
He didn't leave welts
as often as my mom.

1:07:26.935 --> 1:07:29.210
She also used the belt.

1:07:29.437 --> 1:07:35.699
♪

1:07:35.719 --> 1:07:38.294
My dad was very
intimidating,

1:07:38.446 --> 1:07:40.037
So I don't think
he had to hit us

1:07:40.057 --> 1:07:42.448
Quite as hard to
get the point across.

1:07:42.467 --> 1:07:44.634
My mom didn't carry that
fear factor with her,

1:07:44.786 --> 1:07:47.211
So I think she
used more force.

1:07:47.230 --> 1:07:51.399
So, you loved them,
and they hit you?

1:07:51.626 --> 1:07:54.460
Yes.

1:07:54.479 --> 1:07:55.628
